reviews.review_text: great show In my opinion, this is the BEST show from 1980.  The tapes sound GREAT.  It is a real treat that it is here for us!  DOWNLOAD And be very very happy! Gone are the days without good tapes, now we have The Archive.

wow what a set list thanks to the one who taped this show.  they have have given us a piece of music history.  such an intimate sounding recording.  at times the clapping can be a little distrating but i am not complaining.  compared to the many generation bootlegs that i used to be grateful for this is a real treat.  i am going to enjoy 10-14-10 a little bit more because of this recording. I just downloaded every song for free.  thanks again.
Like it, can't love it. Although stellar in spots, this is a very spacey show and good rather than spectacular. Recording not bad, not great. A lot more audience than band, frequently.
